{"word":"παροικέω","slug":"παροικέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παροιϰέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οἰκέω\">οἰκέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘live in a strange place’, <b>live <a href='B:650 11:9'>Hb 11:9</a></b> (if <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a></el> = <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a></el>, but <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> 2); <b>visit <a href='B:490 24:18'>Lk 24:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> migrate</b> <el>παρῴϰησεν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> γῆν τῆς ἐπαγγελίας <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὡς\">ὡς</a> ἀλλοτρίαν</el> went as a sojourner to the land of promise as to an alien place <b><a href='B:650 11:9'>Hb 11:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πάροδος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παροικία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}